dct_title_s: Map Showing Location of New Bulkhead as Constructed by Mulroy-Cook Co.
dct_description_sm: Map shows the current bulkhead location & the new bulkhead, which is at the U.S. pierhead and bulkhead line.
At the northernmost point is the Passaic River, easternmost is the PA R.R. bridge, south and east is the property line of Mulroy-Cook Co..
